N’PY

   N’PY, the tourist industry leader in the Pyrenees, brings together 8
   ski stations, all different and proud of their territory. To their
   customers, they exude a passion for the mountains and for skiing.
   With N’PY, internet users can now book their Pyrenees skiing holiday in
   a few clicks on a single site. More than 100 service providers are
   present (accommodation, skiing lessons, ski-passes, tourist sites,
   massage, activities, etc.) Availability is calculated in real time and
   no commission is charged on sales.
   Forget the middleman and book your holiday 100% ‘à la carte’ with N’PY!
